# Bundled Core ML pipeline assets — populated by scripts/sync-assets.sh
# (~724 MB; some weight blobs exceed GitHub's 100 MB single-file cap).
# To rebuild Resources/ locally: run `./scripts/sync-assets.sh` from the
# project root, which copies mlpackages, voice_kv_states, and tokenizer.model
# from /Users/system-backup/dev_local/pocket-tts-core-ml-conversion/.
pocket-tts-macos/Resources/

